---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="For Businesses — AI Copyright Compliance Guide" description="Using AI in your business? Stay compliant, avoid lawsuits, and protect your content. Free tools, compliance guides, and risk assessment.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-blue-900 to-slate-900 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-400/20 text-blue-300 text-sm font-semibold rounded-full mb-4">For Businesses</span>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
        Using AI in Your Business?<br/>
        <span class="text-blue-400">Stay Compliant. Avoid Lawsuits.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-blue-100 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-8">
        AI-generated content may not be copyrightable. Your competitors can legally copy it. The EU AI Act requires disclosure. Here's how to navigate it all.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="#risks" class="px-6 py-3 bg-blue-500 text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-400 transition-colors">Assess My Risk →</a>
        <a href="#compliance" class="px-6 py-3 bg-white/10 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors">Compliance Checklist</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 1: Risks -->
  <section id="risks" class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-text mb-3">Know Your Risks</h2>
    <p class="text-text-muted mb-8">If your business uses AI to generate content, you face these legal risks:</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-100 rounded-xl p-5">
        <div class="text-2xl mb-2">🚫</div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-red-900 text-sm mb-2">No Copyright Protection</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-red-700 leading-relaxed">Purely AI-generated content cannot be copyrighted. Competitors can legally copy your AI marketing materials, blog posts, and images.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-100 rounded-xl p-5">
        <div class="text-2xl mb-2">⚠️</div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-amber-900 text-sm mb-2">Disclosure Requirements</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-amber-700 leading-relaxed">The EU AI Act requires transparency about AI use. Failing to disclose can result in fines up to €35 million or 7% of global revenue.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-100 rounded-xl p-5">
        <div class="text-2xl mb-2">⚖️</div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-purple-900 text-sm mb-2">Infringement Liability</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-purple-700 leading-relaxed">If your AI tool was trained on copyrighted data, you could face vicarious liability claims. Anthropic faces $1.5B+ in claims.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2: Tools -->
  <section class="bg-slate-50 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-text mb-3">Free Compliance Tools</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted mb-8">Practical tools to help your business stay compliant — no signup required.</p>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <a href="/tools/ai-disclosure-generator" class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <div class="text-3xl">📝</div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-text group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">AI Disclosure Generator</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mt-1">Generate a professional AI use disclosure for your website. Choose from corporate, friendly, or legal tone.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-primary font-semibold text-sm shrink-0">Generate →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/ai-copyright-checker" class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <div class="text-3xl">⚖️</div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-text group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Copyright Risk Assessment</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mt-1">Answer 6 questions about how your business uses AI. Get a personalized risk level and recommendations.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-primary font-semibold text-sm shrink-0">Assess Risk →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/robots-txt-ai-blocker" class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <div class="text-3xl">🤖</div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-text group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Protect Your Content From AI Scraping</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mt-1">Block AI crawlers from scraping your proprietary content for model training.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-primary font-semibold text-sm shrink-0">Block Crawlers →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3: Compliance Checklist -->
  <section id="compliance" class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-text mb-3">AI Copyright Compliance Checklist</h2>
    <p class="text-text-muted mb-8">Essential steps for any business using AI:</p>

    <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">1</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">Audit your AI usage</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Document which teams use AI, what tools, and for what content types.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">2</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">Create an AI use policy</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Define acceptable use, required human oversight, and disclosure rules for employees.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">3</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">Add AI disclosure to your website</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Use our <a href="/tools/ai-disclosure-generator" class="text-primary hover:underline">free generator</a> to create a compliant disclosure statement.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">4</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">Ensure human creative input</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Add substantial human editing to AI outputs if you want copyright protection.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">5</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">Protect your own content from AI scraping</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Block AI crawlers from your proprietary content using <a href="/tools/robots-txt-ai-blocker" class="text-primary hover:underline">robots.txt rules</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">6</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">Monitor legal developments</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">AI copyright law is changing fast. Stay updated with our <a href="/blog" class="text-primary hover:underline">news section</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/learn/ai-copyright-compliance-business" class="inline-block mt-6 px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-white font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-primary-dark transition-colors">Read Full Compliance Guide →</a>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4: What the Law Says -->
  <section class="bg-slate-50 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-text mb-8">What the Law Says</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/laws/united-states" class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="text-xl mb-2">🇺🇸</div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-text mb-1">United States</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Human authorship required. AI output = public domain. Fair use debates ongoing.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/laws/european-union" class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="text-xl mb-2">🇪🇺</div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-text mb-1">European Union</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">AI Act in force. Transparency required. Fines up to €35M for non-compliance.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/laws/united-kingdom" class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="text-xl mb-2">🇬🇧</div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-text mb-1">United Kingdom</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Computer-generated works provision. Code of Practice in development.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/laws" class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="text-xl mb-2">🌍</div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-text mb-1">All Countries</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Compare AI copyright laws across 6 jurisdictions.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Newsletter -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-2">Weekly AI Compliance Updates</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mb-5">New regulations, rulings, and practical guidance for your legal and content teams.</p>
      <form class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 max-w-md mx-auto">
        <input type="email" placeholder="work@company.com" class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-slate-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary" />
        <button type="submit" class="px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-white font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-primary-dark transition-colors">Subscribe Free</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
